        <li><a href="/components/sheet" class="text-primary hover:underline">Sheet</a> — A panel that slides in from the edge for supplementary content.</li>
        <li><a href="/components/drawer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Drawer</a> — A bottom-sheet style overlay, ideal for mobile-friendly interactions.</li>
        <li><a href="/components/popover" class="text-primary hover:underline">Popover</a> — A lightweight overlay anchored to a trigger, for non-modal content.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

